room_title: Escape room "The Facility" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
review: This room is fun for newer escapees because it is a good level of difficulty and easy to follow.  It doesn't have any surprises, but having one person in a different room at first was a cool experience.

room_title: Escape room "The Facility" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
review: We went with friends to do the Facility room and it was so wonderful! So many pieces, switches, electronics, cryptic messages, it was extraordinary and we can't wait to go back.
